Cornucopia Resources Ltd said anextensive drill and sampling program will begin in mid-April atits Ivanhoe gold property in north central Nevada.    It said it will seek to increase the present reserves ofeight mln short tons grading 0.045 ounce of gold per ton thathad been found by USX Corp &lt;X> on a small portion of the13,.000 acre property, determine the location of possiblehigh-grade ore zones at depth and test other targets. Reuter&#3;